      • isModelGRN

        private static boolean isModelGRN(org.sbml.jsbml.Model model)
        This is the main test for the model in the SBML. Depending on the answer all the GRN functionality is available or not. It checks the species SBOterms and the products and modifier SBOterms for the reactions.

                    org.sbml.jsbml.Model model)
        Test if all reaction SBO terms are set and in the allowed values for GRNs. Than tests if the products and modfiers have SBO terms and are in the allowed values for GRNs.
